{"product_id":"the-divine-vision-krishna-devotional-3-piece-set","title":"The Divine Vision | Krishna | Devotional | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"526\" data-end=\"728\"\u003eBring divine calm and spiritual presence into your space with this Krishna 3-Panel Split Wall Art, featuring a close-up of His sacred golden eyes and luminous tilak in a soft painterly devotional style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"1003\"\u003eDesigned with a matte gouache-inspired finish and rich blue tones, this artwork creates a serene focal point above desks, workstations, bedrooms, or meditation corners. The split-panel layout adds a modern aesthetic touch while preserving the sacred emotion of the artwork.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1005\" data-end=\"1158\"\u003eThe warm golden eyes, subtle blush tones, and soft lighting create a peaceful yet powerful presence that transforms any wall into a devotional sanctuary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1160\" data-end=\"1163\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1188\"\u003eWhat You’ll Receive\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1190\" data-end=\"1342\"\u003e• 1 Set = 3 Split Panels\u003cbr data-start=\"1214\" data-end=\"1217\"\u003e• High-detail matte print finish\u003cbr data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1252\"\u003e• Vibrant yet soft devotional color tones\u003cbr data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1296\"\u003e• Modern minimal layout with spiritual depth\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1344\" data-end=\"1347\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1374\"\u003eSize \u0026amp; Finishing Note\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1376\" data-end=\"1530\"\u003eWe print on full sheets and manually trim white borders for a clean edge-to-edge finish.\u003cbr data-start=\"1464\" data-end=\"1467\"\u003eFinal dimensions may vary slightly (±0.5 inch) due to trimming.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1532\" data-end=\"1535\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1558\"\u003eInstallation Note\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1560\" data-end=\"1670\"\u003eFrames and wall tapes are not included.\u003cbr data-start=\"1599\" data-end=\"1602\"\u003eYou may add our wall-stick option at checkout for easy installation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003chr data-start=\"1672\" data-end=\"1675\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 data-start=\"1677\" data-end=\"1692\"\u003ePerfect For\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1806\"\u003e• Desk setups\u003cbr data-start=\"1707\" data-end=\"1710\"\u003e• Meditation corners\u003cbr data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"1733\"\u003e• Living room feature walls\u003cbr data-start=\"1760\" data-end=\"1763\"\u003e• Devotional spaces\u003cbr data-start=\"1782\" data-end=\"1785\"\u003e• Spiritual gifting\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51427341566248,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51427341599016,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51427341631784,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/TheDivineVisionKrishnaDevotional3PieceSet_1.webp?v=1770966815","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/the-divine-vision-krishna-devotional-3-piece-set","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}